4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. It lasts 16 weeks with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will learn about Windows, Linux, network and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis, while mastering data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Successful graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, which is recognized by various institutions. Classes are conducted in English or Spanish. 

